The Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) on Thursday summoned emergency meeting of the National Executive Committee. Details of the meeting were not revealed but the meeting is scheduled for Friday this week.
PDP National Secretary, Sen. Umaru Ibrahim Tsauri, in a Special Announcement of an emergency NEC meeting on Thursday, declared: “All members of the PDP National Executive Committee(NEC) are hereby invited to an emergency meeting of the NEC tomorrow, Friday, 17th January, 2020.
“Venue is NEC Hall, PDP National Secretariat, Wadata Plaza, Abuja and time is 10 a.m.
“Members are enjoined to attend as the meeting will discuss the state of the nation.”

			
